1528385125_1AHEQxyRG9s6owyJHShB4U4rg9GL5.body: [Bandcamp](https://bandcamp.com/), many bands there set the price of their albums to $0, so supporting them or not depending on yourself and your pocket ;) [Jamando](https://www.jamendo.com/) is a great place for legal free music, Archive.org is another wonderful place, someone also [mirrors/archives Jamendo albums](https://archive.org/details/jamendo-albums) there. The ultra music pirate paradise is Youtube -> `youtube-dl`, if you agree...
